{
  "abstract": "This technical note is intended for use by small-scale rural entrepreneurs,\r\nbusiness people and community-based organizations interested in\r\ngroundnut seed production and marketing and groundnut processing and\r\nmarketing. It is targeted to people with little to no formal training or experience\r\nin small-scale business. It focuses on the establishment and management\r\nof small scale businesses. It does not address the technical aspects of\r\ngroundnut seed production or processing. Manuals on technical aspects\r\nof producing seed or processing groundnut may be available from other\r\norganizations.\r\nTwo illustrative examples from a groundnut seed producer and groundnut\r\noil and cakes processor will be used throughout the technical note.",
